[The original posting said: "Health authorities are warning people to take
care in spas after seven Melbourne boys caught hepatitis A in a domestic
spa hot tub." That threw me off a bit and stimulated me to ask for more
information; I wondered where the index case was. I checked out the web
site address kindly sent by Mark Veitch. The report indicates that seven
boys became ill (one the night of the spa party and six a month or more
after that). Thus, six (not seven) boys caught the virus in the spa; one
(the index case) already was infected when he entered the spa. - Mod.CHC
......................................chc/es
